snippet.title: Earth: 9000 - Gameplay - Wave 25
snippet.description:
Earth: 9000 - Quick vid of Wave 25 which is pretty challenging the first few times you get up that high, but with all my upgrades quick work is made of the enemy ships.

The Micro Rail with it's upgrades burns 'em all down pretty fast. Turned on Lunar Devastation (purple moon shots) to handle stuff I wasn't focused on and more than liberal use of the Panic Launcher (those green heat seekers) finishes them all off quite well.
